{"tid":2163611,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第一屆蘋果日報創意廣告大賽","createTime":"2020-08-18T18:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T12:28:38.000Z","uid":5268,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f894aa5005572bf599e2f8d5ace25219ece427db","tid":2163611,"uid":5268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:48:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\">點解要撐蘋果廣告商？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n近排武漢肺炎已經令到市面零售生意慘淡，<br />\n特別係7婆暫停晚市之後更加令到食肆雪上加霜。<br />\n但面對被強權打壓既蘋果，<br />\n唔少商家係復市遙遙無期既情況下，<br />\n都竟然即刻課金用成幾萬銀落廣告支持蘋果，<br />\n所以你撐蘋果，我地撐你，就係咁簡單。<br />\n我地要比人睇到黃圈既經濟實力，吸引更多商家成為我地同路人<br />\n<br />\n係蘋果落廣告 = 爆買<br />\n係CCTVB落廣告 = 罷買<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\">我地可以做d咩？</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你撐蘋果，我地撐你，就係咁簡單。<br />\n<span class=\"red\"> &middot;Like爆 佢地social media,吸引更多商家見到成效係蘋果落廣告<br />\n &middot;bookmark定，以後有機會優先幫襯</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">P.S.可能因為呢排蘋果真係多左好多廣告，攤薄左大家熱情；唔少冷門黃店/小店係蘋果落左廣告，但宣傳效用甚微，幾乎冇乜人知！所以如果呢個post反應好，我會再開post專門介紹係蘋果落左廣告但成效不大黃圈小店！</span>"},{"pid":"cab93c90957bc0ecb5232e491b2a65e0f0072a37","tid":2163611,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sz1ax0e.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsz1ax0e.gif&h=67bb215e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7651472e4ffee61cae02c6bedade5a845cd64a5c","tid":2163611,"uid":5268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T18:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HuW9OyP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHuW9OyP.png&h=804b86e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mZ0R1TR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmZ0R1TR.png&h=aba64dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>白紙篇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n拿，風水命理呢家野，就好講緣分既。俗語都有講，天機不可洩露，所以梁師傅落個白紙廣告絕對係合情合理。但日希聯盟呢個留白就令人有d匪夷所思，係個設計師Sick leave，定係個老細係王苑之Fan呢?<br />\n<br />\n玄機閣梁善行師傅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/yuenkeikwok88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fyuenkeikwok88&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5tey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=743dfb3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/yuenkeikwok88</a><br />\n<br />\n日希聯盟（移民）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/immialliance\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fimmialliance&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5tey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=6491f451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/immialliance</a>"},{"pid":"dab6629e2b18e6ca1d4cabef7f4d8660d448cb72","tid":2163611,"uid":5268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T19:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89un8B5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89un8B5.png&h=c866fe0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">潮文篇</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n今日啱啱買咗一疊蘋果日報，依份係香港最高等級royal級既報紙，買咗$10，一共有70份廣告睇。<br />\n<br />\n你唔使專登買都可以到睇得曬所有落係蘋果既廣告，因為我地每日都會有廣告整合Post，一個價錢，全港線上線下曝光機會，請即刻聯絡蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\nRaw Fruits 和富水果<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rawfruitshk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frawfruitshk%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5tey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=6ef6a317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rawfruitshk/</a>"},{"pid":"0cae86d26262c4db8274d6e950ef7088210a5e14","tid":2163611,"uid":5268,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T19:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4j0yvQ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4j0yvQ4.png&h=a04a6c0e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">模仿篇</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一睇呢位巴打就係模仿達人，放盪不羈既劉海，配上呢個謎之笑容同埋佛系手勢，<br />\n讓人尷尬之餘又帶有d神秘感。雖然唔知模仿鄧家彪同賣花茶有咩關係，<br />\n<br />\n但我見佢地仲有好多自家製花茶，如果喜歡花茶、水果茶既巴打絲打不妨留意下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南堂黑糖花茶<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nantongtea/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnantongtea%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5tey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=d1b6b594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nantongtea/</a><br />\n<br />\n茶後說<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/aftertea.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Faftertea.hk%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5tey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=2347fe7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/aftertea.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"8d403ad2a89ce9f97da6901eb3865b16d80de6de","tid":2163611,"uid":5268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T19:05:54.000Z","msg":"唔記得講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大部分報紙圖片來源夕楓巴打同隔離post"},{"pid":"194093848ab68326ee6599cf40f687465fa770cd","tid":2163611,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T19:07:17.000Z","msg":"物理治療工會嗰個幾好"},{"pid":"9a07d3a58ce12a0725da01e413ff383c4950fb15","tid":2163611,"uid":5268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T19:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8dsAiC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8dsAiC.png&h=0b35aac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">復古風</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n本期精選廣告，簡單、直接，特別係中間果幾個藝術字配埋深褐色，<br />\n簡直洋溢住一股濃烈既街邊設計師風格。Btw, 佢地既咖啡堅好飲，旺角、屯門都有分店，行過不妨坐底嘆下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMy Little Coffee<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/MYLITTLECOFFEE.HK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMYLITTLECOFFEE.HK%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5tey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=5180c342\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://w